Editor’s note: This livestream has ended. You may wacth the recording above. JOHANNESBURG – SuperSport briefed the media on an incident that saw former Springbok Ashwin Willemse walking off set on Saturday. Willemse slammed fellow presenters Naas Botha and Nick Mallett on air saying he will not be patronised by two individuals who played during the apartheid era. Willemse expressed disappointment at how throughout his coaching career he had been labelled a quota player. SuperSport said it is investigating the incident. eNCA